		<Row Tag="LOC_TRAIT_LEADER_LW_SCIENCE_NAME" Language="zh_Hans_CN"><Text>科学白板</Text></Row>
		<Row Tag="LOC_TRAIT_LEADER_LW_SCIENCE_DESCRIPTION" Language="en_US"><Text>+1 [ICON_SCIENCE] Science from City Center.[NEWLINE]Improvements: +1 after Writing, +2 after Education, +3 after Chemistry.</Text></Row>
		<Row Tag="LOC_TRAIT_LEADER_LW_SCIENCE_DESCRIPTION" Language="zh_Hans_CN"><Text>市中心+1[ICON_SCIENCE]科技。[NEWLINE]解锁写作后改良设施+1[ICON_SCIENCE]科技，教育后+2，化学后+3。</Text></Row>
		<Row Tag="LOC_LEADER_LW_CULTURE_NAME" Language="en_US"><Text>Culture Player</Text></Row>
