		<Row Tag="LOC_TRAIT_LEADER_LW_CULTURE_NAME" Language="zh_Hans_CN"><Text>文学白板</Text></Row>
		<Row Tag="LOC_TRAIT_LEADER_LW_CULTURE_DESCRIPTION" Language="en_US"><Text>+1 [ICON_CULTURE] Culture from City Center (+1 more after Political Philosophy).[NEWLINE]Improvements: +1 after Drama & Poetry, +2 after Humanism, +3 after Mass Media.</Text></Row>
		<Row Tag="LOC_TRAIT_LEADER_LW_CULTURE_DESCRIPTION" Language="zh_Hans_CN"><Text>市中心+1[ICON_CULTURE]文化。解锁政治哲学后市中心再+1[ICON_CULTURE]。[NEWLINE]解锁戏剧与诗歌后改良设施+1[ICON_CULTURE]文化，人文主义后+2，大众媒体后+3。</Text></Row>
		<Row Tag="LOC_LEADER_LW_THEOLOGY_NAME" Language="en_US"><Text>Theology Player</Text></Row>
