		<Row Tag="LOC_TRAIT_LEADER_LW_THEOLOGY_NAME" Language="en_US"><Text>Theology</Text></Row>
		<Row Tag="LOC_TRAIT_LEADER_LW_THEOLOGY_NAME" Language="zh_Hans_CN"><Text>神学白板</Text></Row>
		<Row Tag="LOC_TRAIT_LEADER_LW_THEOLOGY_DESCRIPTION" Language="en_US"><Text>+2 [ICON_FAITH] Faith from City Center.[NEWLINE]Improvements: +1 after Mysticism, +2 after Theology, +3 after Reformed Church.</Text></Row>
		<Row Tag="LOC_TRAIT_LEADER_LW_THEOLOGY_DESCRIPTION" Language="zh_Hans_CN"><Text>市中心+2[ICON_FAITH]信仰。[NEWLINE]解锁神秘主义后改良设施+1[ICON_FAITH]信仰，神学后+2，归正会后+3。</Text></Row>
		<Row Tag="LOC_LEADER_LW_AGRICULTURE_NAME" Language="en_US"><Text>Agriculture Player</Text></Row>
