		<Row Tag="LOC_TRAIT_LEADER_LW_AGRICULTURE_NAME" Language="zh_Hans_CN"><Text>农业白板</Text></Row>
		<Row Tag="LOC_TRAIT_LEADER_LW_AGRICULTURE_DESCRIPTION" Language="en_US"><Text>+1 [ICON_FOOD] Food +1 [ICON_HOUSING] Housing from City Center (+1 Food each after Pottery, Irrigation).[NEWLINE]Improvements: +1 after Code of Laws, +2 after Feudalism, +3 after Replaceable Parts.</Text></Row>
		<Row Tag="LOC_TRAIT_LEADER_LW_AGRICULTURE_DESCRIPTION" Language="zh_Hans_CN"><Text>市中心+1[ICON_FOOD]粮食+1[ICON_HOUSING]住房。解锁制陶术、灌溉后市中心各再+1[ICON_FOOD]。[NEWLINE]解锁法典后改良设施+1[ICON_FOOD]粮食，封建主义后+2，零件规格化后+3。</Text></Row>
		<Row Tag="LOC_LEADER_LW_INDUSTRY_NAME" Language="en_US"><Text>Industry Player</Text></Row>
