		<Row Tag="LOC_TRAIT_LEADER_LW_INDUSTRY_NAME" Language="zh_Hans_CN"><Text>工业白板</Text></Row>
		<Row Tag="LOC_TRAIT_LEADER_LW_INDUSTRY_DESCRIPTION" Language="en_US"><Text>+1 [ICON_PRODUCTION] Production from City Center (+1 each after Craftsmanship, Electricity).[NEWLINE]Improvements: +1 after Apprenticeship, +2 after Industrialization, +3 after Nuclear Fission.</Text></Row>
		<Row Tag="LOC_TRAIT_LEADER_LW_INDUSTRY_DESCRIPTION" Language="zh_Hans_CN"><Text>市中心+1[ICON_PRODUCTION]生产力。解锁技艺、电力后市中心各再+1[ICON_PRODUCTION]。[NEWLINE]解锁学徒后改良设施+1[ICON_PRODUCTION]生产力，工业化后+2，核裂变后+3。</Text></Row>
		<Row Tag="LOC_LEADER_LW_COMMERCE_NAME" Language="en_US"><Text>Commerce Player</Text></Row>
