		<Row Tag="LOC_TRAIT_LEADER_LW_COMMERCE_DESCRIPTION" Language="en_US"><Text>+2 [ICON_GOLD] Gold from City Center (+1 each after Currency, Banking).[NEWLINE]Improvements: +1 after Foreign Trade, +2 after Mercantilism, +3 after Capitalism.</Text></Row>
		<Row Tag="LOC_TRAIT_LEADER_LW_COMMERCE_DESCRIPTION" Language="zh_Hans_CN"><Text>市中心+2[ICON_GOLD]金币。解锁货币、银行业后市中心各再+1[ICON_GOLD]。[NEWLINE]解锁对外贸易后改良设施+1[ICON_GOLD]金币，重商主义后+2，资本主义后+3。</Text></Row>
