		<Row Tag="LOC_TRAIT_LEADER_LW_MILITARY_DESCRIPTION" Language="en_US"><Text>+1 [ICON_GOLD] Gold from City Center.[NEWLINE]+1 [ICON_STRENGTH] Combat Strength per unlock: Military Tradition, Bronze Working, Iron Working, Military Engineering, Tactics, Military Science (max +6).</Text></Row>
		<Row Tag="LOC_TRAIT_LEADER_LW_MILITARY_DESCRIPTION" Language="zh_Hans_CN"><Text>市中心+1[ICON_GOLD]金币。[NEWLINE]解锁军事传统、铸铜术、炼铁术、军事工程学、战术、军事学后各给军事单位+1[ICON_STRENGTH]战斗力（最高+6）。</Text></Row>
